{"tid":2369408,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"盧建民獄中呼籲港人行山應量力而為 愛護鄉郊","createTime":"2021-01-17T06:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T09:43:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"65e387f6ca75cd57846eeffb978c9416b18f3f30","tid":2369408,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Y19mulZob3wa4uv4iiS6Cx30d8Y=/802x905/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3H3EQTEXWJAHTKXRUGJ6XTYKC4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FY19mulZob3wa4uv4iiS6Cx30d8Y%3D%2F802x905%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3H3EQTEXWJAHTKXRUGJ6XTYKC4.png&h=26432bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市區疫情反覆加上近期天氣宜人，唔少市民都會選擇假日去郊野公園散心兼呼吸吓新鮮空氣。不過，未必每個人遠足前都會做足準備。2018年因旺角騷亂而遭重判7年的盧建民，早排就專登喺獄中寫信，好激動咁提醒港人行山要量力而為，因為最近每逢假期同周日，都會見到「送中服務隊」不停往返大嶼山，仲不時喺獄中上空飛過。佢仲話，千祈唔好誤信KOL同電視台嘅行山路線推介喎。<br />\n<br />\n由盧建民創辦嘅Facebook專頁「影攝食」，最近就Post一張相信係盧本人寫嘅親筆信。盧喺信入面話，佢每逢星期日或公眾假期，都會喺塘福懲教所球場，望到又名「送中服務隊」嘅飛行服務隊直升機，不斷喺鳳凰山一帶盤旋，「究竟是甚麼人令到直升機如此頻繁地盤旋呢？原來就是一班沒有行山經驗的自私港人貢獻！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/2LXLOKVGGFEODPLPWRN27VQQUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2F2LXLOKVGGFEODPLPWRN27VQQUM%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHCLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=48755abe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2F2LXLOKVGGFEODPLPWRN27VQQUM%2F&h=01ccfc6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/2LXLOKVGGFEODPLPWRN27VQQUM/</a>"},{"pid":"6334162b782033ff1710fc2965a4b3192ae267f1","tid":2369408,"uid":306614,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"連坐緊監嘅都知部分自私撚搞亂香港山頭<br />\n根據我嘅觀察，好多自私撚都係藍絲廢老"},{"pid":"596727175cd8cc34fc053579e94f